]","headword":"berth"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.座（铺）位，卧铺"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.为…提供铺位"}]},{"number":1082,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"◎berth ticket卧铺票/upper berth上铺"},{"type":"entry","text":"bunk [bʌŋk]","headword":"bunk"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.铺位，卧铺"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.为…提供铺位"},{"type":"note","text":"◎lower bunk下铺"},{"type":"entry","text":"schedule [ˈʃedʒuːl]","headword":"schedule"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.时刻表"},{"type":"note","text":"◎flight schedule航班时刻表"},{"type":"entry","text":"train timetable 火车时刻表","headword":"train timetable"},{"type":"entry","text":"book the ticket 订票","headword":"book the ticket"},{"type":"entry","text":"booking office 售票处","headword":"booking office"},{"type":"entry","text":"adult ticket 成人票","headword":"adult ticket"},{"type":"entry","text":"student ticket 学生票","headword":"student ticket"},{"type":"entry","text":"soft sleeper ticket 软卧票","headword":"soft sleeper ticket"},{"type":"entry","text":"hard seat ticket 硬座票","headword":"hard seat ticket"},{"type":"entry","text":"pull in 进站","headword":"pull in"},{"type":"entry","text":"slow down 减速","headword":"slow down"},{"type":"entry","text":"behind schedule 晚点","headword":"behind schedule"},{"type":"entry","text":"carsick [ˈkɑːsɪk]","headword":"carsick"}]},{"number":1083,"blocks":[{"type":"definition","text":"a.晕车的"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Could I change to the sleeper berth? （我能换到卧铺吗？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Sorry, all the berths are booked. （抱歉，所有卧铺都已经订出"},{"type":"text","text":"了。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Would you like an upper berth or a lower berth? （你想要上铺还"},{"type":"text","text":"是下铺？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：A lower berth, please. （请给我下铺。）"}]}]}